name: AI Created Her Face
description: AI created her face, it really did it. Imagine a day, in fact it is today, when AI can generate its own face, change it slightly, and in each time AI understands more what pleases us. Just look at her eyes. Golden curtains switching back and forth, exposing the face of AI, the face that AI created for her, for you . This is "AI created her face". We are living the future. Today. Now.  The constraint is that this NFT art piece can only be simultaneously in 21 different metaverses in art exhibits, thus it is limited edition 21. When you have got enough of her eyes, the secondary is waiting, and the magical number 21 is again filled by somebody else. The artist, me, @tomivisual, promise to do my best to visit gallery openings where this piece is exhibited, time and situations permitting. You can always invite me for a visit to your metaverse, and I will be happy to see her eyes again. And yes, her face, eyes, hair, she is generated by AI. I did the rest.
